data.description: Enjoy this luxurious two-story vacation and investment townhome fully furnished includes 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a combination of living/dining, and a kitchen/family room perfect for entertaining. Additional space includes a large, covered patio and a spacious primary suite. Perfect home to relax with family and friends. Families can head out to the covered patio and enjoy Florida’s views and weather. Highly energy-efficient home features 42-inch maple cabinetry, quartz countertops (kitchen and bathrooms), stainless steel appliances, security system and faux-wood blinds. Enjoy Champions Gate Resort Orlando (Oasis Club) with a resort-style pool, spa, 7 tennis courts, basketball, fitness center and on-site concierge. Other amenities will include a lazy river, waterslides, swim-up bar, waterfalls, beach entry, spa, splash pad, grill, bar, fitness area, theater, game room, tiki bar and cabanas. Simply relax by the pool and watch your family have the time of their life. All of these amenities plus all seven tennis courts are included in HOA fees. Very conveniently located and close to Disney Theme Parks. Short-term rentals allowed. High occupancy and booking volume!
